      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BE MY TIGER (4) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (24.89) at Sale in a Mix 6/7. Lines up from box 4 for the first time. Can go on with it. DR. NAKITA (1) hit the frame two back then broke through last time by 1.75 lengths (24.56) at this track over 425m. Nicely drawn here. Yet to win here but has run some good races. Rates a leading chance again. HOT HONEY (5) is rarely out of the finish, recording seven places from 12 starts. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when second (22.97) at Warragul. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Expected to feature again. RIO BON BON (7) was a huge winner last start. Sure to run well again.",
